:::::::::::::::::::::::commands For EBS:::::::::::::::::

To check and mount filesystem:

=> lsblk
=> file -s /dev/xvdf

=> mkfs -t xfs /dev/xvdf
=> file -s /dev/xvdf

=> cd /apps

=> mkdir -p /apps/volume/new-volume

=> mount /dev/xvdf/apps/volume/new-volume

=> df -h 

To increase the ebs size 

 =>  xfs_growfs /dev/xvdf (or) resize2fs /dev/xvdf
 
 => df -h 

